        	<div class="why-cho_inner">
        	<h2>Software Development</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="images/magic-rabbit.jpg" height=300 width=330>

From its beginnings, WonderOps has supported building the ideas of entrepreneurs with software development. Today, we work with our clients of all sizes to build web and mobile based software in technologies such as Java, node.js, Ruby on Rails, Android and iOS. Our expertise goes beyond just developing code. We have experience in working with clients in DevOps, pipeline automation and Agile development. We want to create awesome code but also deliver continuously and deploy frequently with less hassle. 

<br><br>

We have several ways we can engage with your company and it's software development needs. We can be part of your team at many levels including software architecture as well as development. Our ideal client is one that has high interest in DevOps. Our team looks for clients where there is a high interest in automation, continuous integration and continuous delivery. We believe in the principals of small, incremental deployments as a foundation for providing high quality releases.

<br><br>

Time to market is essential for software product development. Companies must consistently deliver value to their customers with high availability and quality code. At WonderOps, we want to help the right customers win in their marketplace through quality software development, highly automated pipelines, and error free release management.   

